%% Diagram: Classic three-state circuit breaker (Nygard / Fowler)
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Closed
    Closed --> Open: failure threshold exceeded<br/>(consecutive errors or error rate)
    Open --> HalfOpen: cool-off timer elapsed
    HalfOpen --> Closed: trial requests succeed
    HalfOpen --> Open: trial requests fail

    note right of Closed
        Requests proxied normally.
        Failure metrics tracked.
    end note
    note right of Open
        Requests fail fast.
        Backend not contacted.
        Saves cascading load.
    end note
    note right of HalfOpen
        Limited probe traffic.
        Decides whether backend recovered.
    end note
